                    <li class="mb-2"><b>Research:</b> Creates new ideas for activities, promotions, and communication. Maintains a strong understanding of the competitors. Identifies and translates market trends and prepare reports / plans accordingly.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2"><b>trategies & Execution:</b>Develops, leads and implements the marketing strategies and this includes assisting and developing 1-3 year plan and objectives.</li>
