                <ul class="list-disc">
                    <li class="mb-2">Ensure to achieve the annual business & projects target.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Manages the marketing budgets for all professional activities and promotions.</li>

                </ul>
                <h3 class="h3 h3-mb  mb-2 ">Non- Financial Aspects</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc">
                    <li class="mb-2">Works independently and cross-functionally, ensuring that direction is aligned with the management.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Works closely and internally in the department and the bank, and through this process to ensure proper alignment. </li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Maintains and develops relationships with key partners</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Ensure projects, marketing promotions & activities to be executed on schedule.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Leads program measurements and accountability measures.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Continually evaluates the performance of marketing tactics and adjusts plans accordingly. </li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Educate and train the teams to be proactive, team-work, and profit driven, solution & target-focused mind set. </li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Provide on a regular basis KPI insights to the teams.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2">Manage and drive teams to maintain high performance.</li>
                </ul>

